SD=Account Recovery
CR= Account Recovery Procedure
BQs=Assessment Writedown Planning Negotiation Restructuring
Handles the recovery of distressed accounts that have exceeded standard late/payment handling but have not yet been fully written off and passed to collections. The restructuring can involve partial write downs and leveraging any tax or other program of assistance that can be applied. The situation is managed until the account is recovered or a decision made to pass the account over to collections
"A non-performing customer account is handed over for recovery after the normal relationship management efforts have failed. Additional authority is provided to renegotiate/structure the account to enable the customer to attempt recovery. This restructuring can result in write downs that need to be booked appropriately"
This service domain handles the restructuring of a distressed account (loan) after standard recovery procedures have been exhausted
CR - Account Recovery Procedure				BQ 1 - Assessment		BQ 2 - Writedown			BQ 3 - Planning		BQ 4 - Negotiation				BQ 5 - Restructuring		
In	Up	Ec	Re	Up	Re	Up	Ec	Re	Up	Re	Up	Ec	Rq	Re	Up	Ec	Re
InCR Initiate the account recovery procedure
UpCR Update details of an active account recovery case
EcCR Accept, reject, verify etc. an active account recovery case
ReCR Retrieve details about an active account recovery case
UpBQ Update details of an active case assessment
ReBQ Retrieve details of an active case assessment
UpBQ Update details of an active case write-down
EcBQ Accept, reject, verify etc. an active case write-down
ReBQ Retrieve details of an active case assessment
UpBQ Update details of an active case recovery plan
ReBQ Retrieve details of an active case recovery plan
UpBQ Update details of an active case negotiation
EcBQ Accept, reject, verify etc. an active case negotiation
RqBQ Request a negotiation for an active recovery case
ReBQ Retrieve details of an active case negotiation
UpBQ Update details of case restructuring tasks
EcBQ Accept, reject, verify etc. case restructuring task
ReBQ Retrieve details of case restructuring tasks